Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.65,0:02:05.55,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你渐渐远去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.44,0:02:07.96,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(320,348)}无论何时 都还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:09.98,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(320,348)}即便一切 天翻地覆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:12.04,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(320,348)}唯有那件 唯有那件
